.Dd August 19, 2021
.Dt LOCALELOCALE 1
.Os
.Sh NAME
.Nm localelocale
.Nd print the device's iOS locale
.Sh SYNOPSIS
.Nm
.Op Fl ilcvh
.Sh DESCRIPTION
.Nm
will print the system locale in the specified format, then exit.
.Sh OPTIONS
.Bl -tag -width indent
.It Fl i , -identifier
Print the locale identifier, this is the default
.It Fl l , -language
Prints the language code for the locale
.It Fl c , -country
Prints the country code for the locale
.It Fl v , -variant
Prints the locale variant
.It Fl h , -help
Prints a help text
.El
.Sh SEE ALSO
.Xr ecidecid 1 ,
.Xr uiduid 1
